plot: 'Color's Notes ' is an independent music documentary film, where artists and musicians of different parts and cultures of the world, were met in Elx's city at the acts and events happened during the celebration of the 10th festival of music and culture MESTIVAL 2005 at Alicante, Spain. The World.   Written by  Xavi tello
